The security detail only saw me and Goodwin together,

218
00:15:00,430 --> 00:15:01,730
没看见你和他
not the two of you.

219
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:07,460
我要宣誓作证的
This is under oath.

220
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:10,490
安德伍德的人是想抹黑我们
Underwood's people are trying to smear us.

221
00:15:10,500 --> 00:15:11,750
这场竞选的全部意义
The whole point of this campaign

222
00:15:11,750 --> 00:15:13,660
