was to be the opposite of Underwood.

223
00:15:13,660 --> 00:15:15,270
我以为你想要这个的
I thought you wanted this.

224
00:15:15,550 --> 00:15:17,440
如果要犯法就不行
Not if it means breaking the law.

225
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,920
你觉得换作他  还会有这种犹豫吗
Do you think he'd even be having this conversation?

226
00:15:21,070 --> 00:15:23,960
你是真正在意法律的  希瑟
You actually care about the law, Heather...

227
00:15:25,100 --> 00:15:27,130
所以该由你来做总统
which is why you need to be president.

228
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:49,450
-安德伍德夫人  -鲍勃  我不知道...
- Mrs. Underwood. - Bob, I didn't realize--

229
00:15:49,450 --> 00:15:52,820
少数党领袖和我正在讨论救市计划
The Leader and I were just discussing the bailout package.

230
00:15:53,170 --> 00:15:55,100
布莱斯总统要我强调一下
President Blythe just wanted me to stress

231
00:15:55,100 --> 00:15:58,780
民主党人当前团结一致的重要性
how important it is that the Democrats stick together right now

232
00:15:59,210 --> 00:16:00,250
弗兰西斯还在...
with Francis being--

233
00:16:00,250 --> 00:16:00,660
不必如此
There's no need.

234
00:16:00,660 --> 00:16:04,510
我刚给议长打了电话  安排紧急投票
I just called the Speaker to schedule an emergency vote.

235
00:16:04,510 --> 00:16:06,740
