I'm sure the President will be pleased.

236
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,880
-弗兰克怎么样  -他还撑着
- How's Frank? - He's hanging in there.

237
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,570
你一定想快点回医院
I'm sure you wanna get back to the hospital.

238
00:16:12,570 --> 00:16:14,830
但谢谢你亲自前来
But thank you for making the personal visit.

239
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,670
牵挂和祈祷与你同在  克莱尔
Thoughts and prayers, Claire.

240
00:16:17,290 --> 00:16:18,340
谢谢你  鲍勃
Thank you, Bob.

241
00:16:18,450 --> 00:16:19,880
