我们不必不和的  杰姬
We don't need to be at odds, Jackie.

245
00:16:38,410 --> 00:16:40,450
你打算每次遭遇我的反对
Do you plan on hanging this over my head

246
00:16:40,470 --> 00:16:42,390
都拿这个来威胁我吗
every time I try to oppose you?

247
00:16:42,400 --> 00:16:44,810
你自己不小心  可怪不得我
You can't fault me for your sloppiness.

248
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:46,610
也就是"是"了
That's a "Yes."

249
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:48,670
只要我们是一边的
As long as we're working together,

250
00:16:48,670 --> 00:16:50,750
你就没什么可担心的
you have nothing to worry about.

251
00:16:56,470 --> 00:16:58,840
总统先生  希望您别过于乐观
Mr. President, I wouldn't get your hopes up.

252
00:16:58,940 --> 00:17:00,130
七国集团的成员们
The members of the G7

