00:17:17,150 --> 00:17:20,230
-你听说了吧  -对  博奇几分钟前来电了
- I'm sure you've heard. - Yes, Birch called a few minutes ago.

261
00:17:20,510 --> 00:17:23,100
我想和你一起去勃兰登堡  凯茜
I'd like to join you in Brandenburg, Cathy.

262
00:17:23,250 --> 00:17:25,630
很感谢你愿意出力
Well, I appreciate you wanting to pitch in,

263
00:17:25,630 --> 00:17:27,360
