266
00:17:32,060 --> 00:17:34,690
-所有人都在场  -弗兰克呢
- Everyone at the same table. - What about Frank?

267
00:17:35,200 --> 00:17:37,560
我在勃兰登堡能派上用场  在这里就不能了
In Brandenburg, I can be useful. I can't here.

268
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:38,580
第一夫人不能
The First Lady cannot

