Mrs. Underwood? Dr. Saxon is on the line.

289
00:19:21,450 --> 00:19:22,540
失陪一下
Excuse me.

290
00:19:29,410 --> 00:19:30,260
喂
Hello?

291
00:19:33,350 --> 00:19:35,340
晚上好  或者说早上好
Good evening, or good morning.

292
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:40,330
