00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:48,240
手术将耗时12到13小时
the surgery is expected to take 12 to 13 hours.

296
00:19:48,540 --> 00:19:50,980
有需要的话我们会向大家更新情况
Uh, we'll update you about the progress if need be,

297
00:19:50,980 --> 00:19:55,010
