00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:16,810
"医疗团队有极大的信心"
"...in the medical team at Jefferson Memorial."

320
00:21:16,810 --> 00:21:19,190
我在祈祷手术成功
I'm praying for a successful procedure,

321
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:23,720
我也请求你们跟我一起为我丈夫
and I ask all of you to join me in praying for my husband,

322
00:21:24,120 --> 00:21:25,360
你们的总统祈祷
your president.

323
00:21:37,620 --> 00:21:39,010
请就坐  邓巴女士
Right over there, Ms. Dunbar.

324
00:21:40,830 --> 00:21:41,870
